- 数组作返回值



## 普通的`For`循环

<img width='688' height='922' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bfd36d95-c808-40d4-bba9-f2a8a7377ea9' />



## `For-Each`循环

- 举例：

```java
public static void main(String[] args){
    int[] arrays = {1,2,3,4,5};

    //JDK1.5，没有下标
    for (int array : arrays) {
        System.out.println(array);
    }
}
```



